de.opendiabetes.vault.container

Class BucketEventTriggers

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.opendiabetes.vault.container.BucketEventTriggers

  • public class BucketEventTriggers
extends java.lang.Object
    This class contains all the HashSets and HashMaps needed during the creation of BucketEntrys and for the computation of internal data.

        public static final java.util.HashSet<VaultEntryType> TRIGGER_EVENT_ACT_TIME_GIVEN

      • TRIGGER_EVENT_ACT_TIME_TILL_NEXT_EVENT

        public static final java.util.HashMap<VaultEntryType,VaultEntryType> TRIGGER_EVENT_ACT_TIME_TILL_NEXT_EVENT
        This HashMap contains all VaultEntryTypes that are onehot and ML-relevant and have an act time till the occurrence of a specific VaultEntryType. The first VaultEntryType is the VaultEntryType with an act time. The second VaultEntryType is the VaultEntryType that ends the act time of the first VaultEntryType. The VaultEntrytype that ends the act time will not change throughout the run time of this program and thus is hardcoded here.

      • TRIGGER_EVENT_ACT_TIME_ONE

        public static final java.util.HashSet<VaultEntryType> TRIGGER_EVENT_ACT_TIME_ONE
        This HashSet contains all VaultEntryTypes that are onehot and ML-relevant and have an act time of only one minute (one BucketEntry).

      • TRIGGER_EVENTS_NOT_YET_SET

        public static final java.util.HashSet<VaultEntryType> TRIGGER_EVENTS_NOT_YET_SET
